#  Sales Data Analysis Project

##  Objective
The objective of this project is to analyze sales data to identify:

- Sales trends over time
- Seasonal effects
- Performance of different product lines
- Customer and country-wise performance
- Deal size contribution to revenue

---

##  Dataset
- Source: Kaggle Sales Dataset (Classic Models Sales Data)
- File Used: sales data.csv
- The dataset contains information about:
  - Orders
  - Product lines
  - Sales amount
  - Customers
  - Countries
  - Deal sizes
  - Order status
  - Time details (Month, Year)

---

##  Tools & Technologies Used

- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Jupyter Notebook (VS Code)

---

##  Project Workflow

### 1️ Data Loading & Exploration
- Loaded dataset using Pandas
- Checked dataset shape and structure
- Identified missing values
- Converted ORDERDATE into datetime format

### 2️ Data Cleaning
- Ensured proper data types
- Removed inconsistencies (if any)

### 3️ Sales Trend Analysis
- Yearly sales trend analysis
- Monthly sales trend analysis
- Identified high-performing months

### 4️ Seasonal Analysis
- Analyzed sales variation across different months
- Observed seasonal spikes in revenue

### 5️ Product Performance Analysis
- Sales by Product Line
- Sales by Deal Size
- Identified best-performing product categories

### 6️ Market Performance Analysis
- Top 10 countries by sales
- Sales by order status
- Top customers by revenue contribution

### 7️ Correlation Analysis
- Generated heatmap to analyze relationships between numerical variables

---

## Key Insights

- Sales show strong seasonal variation.
- Certain product lines contribute significantly more revenue.
- Large deal sizes generate higher overall sales.
- Some countries dominate total revenue.
- Order status impacts total revenue realization.

---

## Visualizations Included

- Yearly Sales Trend (Line Chart)
- Monthly Sales Trend (Line Chart)
- Sales by Product Line (Bar Chart)
- Sales by Deal Size (Bar Chart)
- Top 10 Countries by Sales
- Sales by Order Status
- Top 10 Customers
- Correlation Heatmap

